{"ts":"2026-06-26T16:38:14.497Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Examining Tool Pages**\n\nI've shifted my focus to the core tool pages: `app/build/blueprint/page.tsx`, `app/build/assessment/page.tsx`, `app/build/roi/page.tsx`, `app/build/proposal/page.tsx`, and `app/build/talk/page.tsx`. Currently, I'm examining each, before moving on to consider `components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx`.\n\n\n**Evaluating Stepper Integration**\n\nI'm now contemplating integrating the reusable `WizardStepperSystem` with the core application pages. I'm excited about the potential to revamp `components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx` or `app/build/blueprint/page.tsx`. Specifically, I am thinking of the opportunity to convert all these pages: Assessment, ROI, Proposal, and Talk to Agent (Intake Console), into multi-step flows. I think this strategy would significantly elevate the user experience.\n\n\n**Designing Assessment Refactor**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on refactoring `app/build/assessment/page.tsx`. I've outlined a 5-step interactive assessment wizard, integrating `WizardStepperSystem` to enhance the user experience. The steps include Data Integration, VPC Isolation, Compliance Telemetry, Fleet Strategy, and Industry Sector. I intend to use the existing `calculateAssessmentScore` function, which accepts `AssessmentAnswers` from `components/build/services.ts`.\n\n\n**Analyzing Assessment Page**\n\nI'm now diving into the specifics of the `calculateAssessmentScore` function and the structure of `AssessmentResult`. The detailed breakdown, particularly `dimensionScores`, is very exciting. I'm focusing on integrating these components with the `WizardStepperSystem` in `app/build/assessment/page.tsx` now.\nI am now developing the steps of the assessment page.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T16:38:14.500Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"qc86vpe3","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/build/assessment/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport { ToolPageShell, ToolInputGroup, ToolOptionGrid, ToolCTA } from \"@/components/build/components\";\nimport { WizardStepperSystem, WizardStep } from \"@/components/build/WizardStepperSystem\";\nimport { calculateAssessmentScore } from \"@/components/build/services\";\nimport { AssessmentAnswers, AssessmentResult, Industry } from \"@/components/build/types\";\nimport { SHARED_INDUSTRY_OPTIONS } from \"@/lib/shared-constants\";\n\nexport default function AssessmentPage() {\n  const initialData: AssessmentAnswers = {\n    dataIntegration: 3,\n    vpcIsolation: 3,\n    complianceTelemetry: 3,\n    fleetStrategy: 3,\n    industry: \"banking\"\n  };\n\n  const steps: WizardStep<AssessmentAnswers>[] = [\n    {\n      id: \"data\",\n      label: \"Data pipelines\",\n      description: \"Define the ingestion schema, connectivity, and caching capabilities of transactional databases.\",\n      duration: \"1 min\",\n      render: ({ data, onChange }) => (\n        <ToolInputGroup label=\"Ingestion & Vector Schema Integration\" valueDisplay={`Level ${data.dataIntegration}/5`} accentColor=\"#009DFF\">\n          <input\n            type=\"range\"\n            min=\"1\"\n            max=\"5\"\n            value={data.dataIntegration}\n            onChange={(e) => onChange({ dataIntegration: Number(e.target.value) })}\n            className=\"w-full accent-[#009DFF]\"\n          />\n          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35 mt-2\">\n            <span>Fragmented Legacy Logs</span>\n            <span>Hardened Vector Cache</span>\n          </div>\n        </ToolInputGroup>\n      )\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"vpc\",\n      label: \"VPC Network Isolation\",\n      description: \"Determine the baseline networking isolation level and tenancy requirements.\",\n      duration: \"1 min\",\n      render: ({ data, onChange }) => (\n        <ToolInputGroup label=\"Network Boundary Isolation Status\" valueDisplay={`Level ${data.vpcIsolation}/5`} accentColor=\"#9D00FF\">\n          <input\n            type=\"range\"\n            min=\"1\"\n            max=\"5\"\n            value={data.vpcIsolation}\n            onChange={(e) => onChange({ vpcIsolation: Number(e.target.value) })}\n            className=\"w-full accent-[#9D00FF]\"\n          />\n          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35 mt-2\">\n            <span>Shared Public Cloud</span>\n            <span>Single-Tenant VPC Enclave</span>\n          </div>\n        </ToolInputGroup>\n      )\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"compliance\",\n      label: \"Compliance Telemetry\",\n      description: \"Configure conversational telemetry and persistent log retention specifications.\",\n      duration: \"1 min\",\n      render: ({ data, onChange }) => (\n        <ToolInputGroup label=\"Real-time Auditing & Observability\" valueDisplay={`Level ${data.complianceTelemetry}/5`} accentColor=\"#E4000F\">\n          <input\n            type=\"range\"\n            min=\"1\"\n            max=\"5\"\n            value={data.complianceTelemetry}\n            onChange={(e) => onChange({ complianceTelemetry: Number(e.target.value) })}\n            className=\"w-full accent-[#E4000F]\"\n          />\n          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35 mt-2\">\n            <span>No Telemetry Sweeps</span>\n            <span>Consensus Compliance Audit</span>\n          </div>\n        </ToolInputGroup>\n      )\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"fleet\",\n      label: \"Multi-Agent Strategy\",\n      description: \"Map execution complexity and agentic task allocation pathways.\",\n      duration: \"1 min\",\n      render: ({ data, onChange }) => (\n        <ToolInputGroup label=\"Agentic Execution & Autonomy Scope\" valueDisplay={`Level ${data.fleetStrategy}/5`} accentColor=\"#00FF9D\">\n          <input\n            type=\"range\"\n            min=\"1\"\n            max=\"5\"\n            value={data.fleetStrategy}\n            onChange={(e) => onChange({ fleetStrategy: Number(e.target.value) })}\n            className=\"w-full accent-[#00FF9D]\"\n          />\n          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35 mt-2\">\n            <span>Ad-hoc Single Tasks</span>\n            <span>Orchestrated Supervisor DAGs</span>\n          </div>\n        </ToolInputGroup>\n      )\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"industry\",\n      label: \"Target Industry\",\n      description: \"Select target operational domain to parse compliance frameworks.\",\n      duration: \"1 min\",\n      render: ({ data, onChange }) => (\n        <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n          <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 uppercase\">Primary Domain Segment</label>\n          <select\n            value={data.industry}\n            onChange={(e) => onChange({ industry: e.target.value as Industry })}\n            className=\"w-full h-11 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-black text-white px-3 focus:border-[#009DFF] outline-none text-xs font-mono\"\n          >\n            {SHARED_INDUSTRY_OPTIONS.map((opt) => (\n              <option key={opt.value} value={opt.value.toLowerCase().replace(\" \", \"-\")}>\n                {opt.label}\n              </option>\n            ))}\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      )\n    }\n  ];\n\n  const summaryItems = (data: AssessmentAnswers) => [\n    { label: \"Data Pipelines\", value: `Level ${data.dataIntegration}` },\n    { label: \"VPC Isolation\", value: `Level ${data.vpcIsolation}` },\n    { label: \"Compliance\", value: `Level ${data.complianceTelemetry}` },\n    { label: \"Agentic Fleet\", value: `Level ${data.fleetStrategy}` },\n    { label: \"Domain Segment\", value: data.industry.toUpperCase(), color: \"#009DFF\" }\n  ];\n\n  const onCompile = (data: AssessmentAnswers) => {\n    return calculateAssessmentScore(data);\n  };\n\n  const renderResult = (data: AssessmentAnswers, result: AssessmentResult, onReset: () => void) => {\n    return (\n      <div className=\"space-y-8 animate-fadeIn\">\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#04060b] text-center space-y-4\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 block\">MATURITY SCORE</span>\n            <span className=\"text-5xl font-extrabold font-mono text-[#009DFF] block\">{result.score}%</span>\n            <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5\">\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block\" style={{ color: result.color }}>\n                {result.level}\n              </span>\n              <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light mt-2\">{result.description}</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#04060b] space-y-6\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider\">Maturity Dimension Vectors</h3>\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              {result.dimensionScores.map((dim, idx) => (\n                <div key={idx} className=\"p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.005] border border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline\">\n                    <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono\">{dim.label}</h4>\n                    <span className=\"text-xs font-bold font-mono text-[#00FF9D]\">Maturity Level {dim.score}/5</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 leading-normal font-light\">{dim.description}</p>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] text-[#009DFF] leading-normal font-light italic font-mono\">Recommendation: {dim.recommendation}</p>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-white/40\">Sovereign baseline calculated deterministically in secure local browser cache memory.</p>\n          <button\n            type=\"button\"\n            onClick={onReset}\n            className=\"px-6 h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold text-white/75 hover:bg-white/5 transition\"\n          >\n            Configure Alternative Vector\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <ToolCTA />\n      </div>\n    );\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <ToolPageShell>\n      <WizardStepperSystem\n        toolName=\"Sovereign AI Readiness Assessor\"\n        category=\"Interactive Diagnostic\"\n        toolDescription=\"Benchmark local data integration, network isolation, compliance loops, and agentic fleet readiness parameters deterministically.\"\n        steps={steps}\n        initialData={initialData}\n        summaryItems={summaryItems}\n        onCompile={onCompile}\n        renderResult={renderResult}\n        metricLabel=\"READINESS AUDIT INDEX\"\n        metricValue=\"AIR-SECURE\"\n      />\n    </ToolPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
