turity {dim.score}/5</span></div>\n                    <p className=\"text-white/50 font-light\">{dim.description}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/30 font-mono font-light\">Calculated locally with zero retention.</p>\n              <button type=\"button\" onClick={onReset} className=\"px-5 h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-semibold text-white/85 hover:bg-white/5 transition uppercase font-mono\">Configure Alternative</button>\n            </div>\n            <ToolCTA />\n          </div>\n        )}\n        metricLabel=\"READINESS INDEX\"\n        metricValue=\"LOCAL-SECURE\"\n      />\n    </ToolPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
